Prerequisite:
1. Node.js - installed
2. json-server - installed
Download json-server from : https://github.com/typicode/json-server

Install "json-server" by using below command

npm install -g json-server

Start "json-server" by using below command

json-server --watch db.json

O/P:
  Resources
  http://localhost:3000/posts
  http://localhost:3000/comments
  http://localhost:3000/profile

  Home
  http://localhost:3000
  
 Edit the db.json created above to have the json data as per your requirement / fake api.
 
 Removed the existing data and ceated own data for testing:
 
 
 


